    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the grill to medium-high</p><p>Slice your <strong>lemongrass </strong>in half lengthways</p><p>Soak the <strong>sliced lemongrass</strong> in cold water \u2013 these are your <strong>lemongrass skewers</strong></p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hue-lemongrass-pork-skewers-with-cauliflower-rice/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Slice <strong>half </strong>your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> into rounds and finely chop the remaining</p><p>Wash, then remove the <strong>leaves </strong>from your<strong> lettuce </strong>(2 per person!)<strong> </strong>and set aside</p><p>Shred the<strong> inner core[s]</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hue-lemongrass-pork-skewers-with-cauliflower-rice/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>white long grain rice </strong>and <strong>cauliflower rice</strong> to a pot with a lid with 110ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [175ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[225ml] </span>cold water and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once done, remove from the heat and set aside (lid on) to steam until serving</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hue-lemongrass-pork-skewers-with-cauliflower-rice/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mince </strong>(remove the paper from the mince if required!),<strong> diced chilli, chopped shallot</strong>,<strong> half</strong> of your <strong>gluten free soy sauce </strong>and <strong>half </strong>of your <strong>fish sauce </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) in a bowl and mix everything together</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hue-lemongrass-pork-skewers-with-cauliflower-rice/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>mince mixture</strong> into 2 per person and press it onto each <strong>lemongrass skewer</strong> to form a long sausage shape</p><p>Add the <strong>lemongrass skewers</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) (use <strong>tin foil</strong> to avoid mess!)</p><p>Place the <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined tray[s] under the grill for 10-15 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hue-lemongrass-pork-skewers-with-cauliflower-rice/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>peanut butter</strong>, <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong>, <strong>remaining gluten free soy sauce </strong>and <strong>remaining fish sauce </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>peanut dipping sauce</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hue-lemongrass-pork-skewers-with-cauliflower-rice/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>carrot & cabbage slaw mix </strong>to a bowl with your <strong>rice vinegar </strong>and the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong>, mix it all together and set aside \u2013 this is your <strong>cabbage & carrot salad</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hue-lemongrass-pork-skewers-with-cauliflower-rice/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Hue lemongrass skewers </strong>with the <strong>peanut dipping sauce</strong>, <strong>cabbage & carrot salad, lettuce leaves </strong>and<strong> cooked cauliflower rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chilli rounds </strong>and <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
